name: Eticketando
tag_list: ticket, rio-de-janeiro, sao-paulo, sao-paolo, rio, ingresso, eventos, eventbrite, event-brite, event, events, cvent, ticketleap, amiando, ticketmaster
overview: Eticketando is the first platform in LATAM enabling event organizers to develop, promote and sell their tickets online. With Eticketando, organizers can use the power of social networks to bring attendees to their events with ease. Anyone planning or attending an event will find an engaging platform to promote efficiently and sell their tickets. For attendees, the Rio de Janeiro based company provides a fast and streamlined experience to search and buy tickets.
